    • Method Detail

      • onIabPurchaseFinished

        void onIabPurchaseFinished(IabResult result,
                         Purchase info)
        Called to notify that an in-app purchase finished. If the purchase was successful, then the sku parameter specifies which item was purchased. If the purchase failed, the sku and extraData parameters may or may not be null, depending on how far the purchase process went.
        Parameters:
        result - The result of the purchase.
        info - The purchase information (null if purchase failed)
